headline: Analysts Continue to View Principal Financial Group (PFG) Cautiously as Sector Cycle Softens
summary: Principal Financial Group (NASDAQ:PFG) is among the 9 Best Life Insurance Stocks to Buy Now. Morgan Stanley increased its price objective for Principal Financial Group (NASDAQ:PFG) from $83 to $87 on November 17, 2025, while maintaining an Underweight rating, as reported by TheFly.
